    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is an absolute gem and has been babied since the day I got it\u2014it\u2019s in truly flawless condition! Seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new and has been loved every mile, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen boasts a linear power delivery through eight individual throttle bodies and is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral dynamics. Finished in Alpine White with a flawless carbon fiber roof, the vehicle exhibits zero oxidation or mechanical fatigue. Comprehensive service records confirm rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS systems operate within factory tolerances. The Fox Red Novillo leather interior remains supple with no bolster wear, reflecting its status as a premier enthusiast-kept example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Clean title. Garage kept. All service records available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
